273
00:13:10.690 --> 00:13:12.910
so I can't just say,

274
00:13:12.910 --> 00:13:14.125
"By the way, are you rich?"

275
00:13:14.125 --> 00:13:15.790
"Yeah, I'm rich."
So, "Okay, great.

