00:16:31.780 --> 00:16:33.910
we saw with the
traditional IPO process.

337
00:16:33.910 --> 00:16:36.280
So if I got this market,

338
00:16:36.280 --> 00:16:38.830
if I'm raising only
up to a $100,000,

339
00:16:38.830 --> 00:16:40.870
then all I need is

340
00:16:40.870 --> 00:16:43.825
a company official to sign
off on the documents.

341
00:16:43.825 --> 00:16:46.600
A company official
like I could just sign

342
00:16:46.600 --> 00:16:50.185
off that just my
disclosures being accurate.

343
00:16:50.185 --> 00:16:52.780
If I want to go up
to a half million,

