00:16:55.015 --> 00:16:58.360
my information reviewed
by a public accountant.

346
00:16:58.360 --> 00:17:00.430
Now, review is
a term of art here.

347
00:17:00.430 --> 00:17:02.695
Review and audit are
two different things.

348
00:17:02.695 --> 00:17:05.935
A review is less costly

349
00:17:05.935 --> 00:17:09.070
far fewer professional hours
