364
00:17:40.720 --> 00:17:46.420
and so that's the idea
here that we're not

365
00:17:46.420 --> 00:17:48.925
making the entrepreneur spend

366
00:17:48.925 --> 00:17:50.830
a tremendous amount
of professional hours

367
00:17:50.830 --> 00:17:52.510
if they're not raising
that much money.

368
00:17:52.510 --> 00:17:55.420
So that is the entrepreneur side.

369
00:17:55.420 --> 00:17:58.540
On the investor side,

370
00:17:58.540 --> 00:18:03.040
they said they are going
to be limited in how

371
00:18:03.040 --> 00:18:04.645
much they can invest

372
00:18:04.645 --> 00:18:07.915
depending on
their wealth and income.

373
00:18:07.915 --> 00:18:11.500
So basically, what it
boils down to is that

374
00:18:11.500 --> 00:18:15.849
if you make up to
a 100,000 bucks,

