400
00:19:32.515 --> 00:19:37.855
Title IV is what people
often refer to as Reg A+.

401
00:19:37.855 --> 00:19:43.075
Reg A+ because there has
been a Reg A for many years.

402
00:19:43.075 --> 00:19:45.955
Reg A+ is just a bit
of a twist on it.

403
00:19:45.955 --> 00:19:50.815
Reg A+ really isn't what anyone
